OL,3,CDigital ID cards for children as young
OL,4,Cas 13, government suggests
OL,6,FChildren as young as 13 could be given
OL,7,Fdigital ID cards when the proposed new
OL,8,Fpolicy becomes law, the government has
OL,9,Fsuggested.
OL,11,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer recently
OL,12,Fannounced that anyone wanting to work
OL,13,Fin the UK will require a digital ID,
OL,14,Fin a bid to crackdown on illegal
OL,15,Fmigration by making it harder for
OL,16,Fasylum seekers to gain employment in
OL,17,FBritain.
