OL,3,CDigital ID cards for children as young
OL,4,Cas 13, government suggests
OL,6,FThe government had previously said all
OL,7,Fover 16s would be required to have
OL,8,Fdigital ID by 2029, though has now
OL,9,Fannounced that it will consult on
OL,10,Fwhether children as young as 13 should
OL,11,Falso be included in the scheme.
OL,13,FExplaining why, the The Department for
OL,14,FScience, Innovation and Technology
OL,15,Fsaid employers will be required to
OL,16,Fcheck everyone's digital ID before
OL,17,Fhiring them and because young
OL,18,Fteenagers can work part-time, "we need
OL,19,Fto consult on whether it should be
OL,20,Foffered to those aged 13 and over".
