OL,6,FAlmost 3 million people have now
OL,7,Fsigned a petition demanding the policy
OL,8,Fis scrapped, but the government has
OL,9,Fdoubled down in its response.
OL,11,FIn its response to the petition, the
OL,12,Fgovernment added: "For clarity, it
OL,13,Fwill not be a criminal offence to not
OL,14,Fhold a digital ID and police will not
OL,15,Fbe able to demand to see a digital ID
OL,16,Fas part of a 'stop and search'."
