OL,4,Cas 13, government suggests
OL,6,FAside from tackling illegal working,
OL,7,Fthe government says digital ID - which
OL,8,Fwill also be known as the Brit Card -
OL,9,Fwill make it easier for people to
OL,10,Faccess government services ` such as
OL,11,Fbenefits or tax records ` without
OL,12,Fneeding to remember multiple logins or
OL,13,Fprovide physical documents.
OL,15,FBut civil liberties group Big Brother
OL,16,FWatch, said digital ID is "fast
OL,17,Fbecoming a digital permit required to
OL,18,Flive our everyday lives".
