OL,3,CDigital ID cards for children as young
OL,4,Cas 13, government suggests
OL,6,FIt's director Silkie Carlo told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "The prospects of enrolling even
OL,8,Fchildren into this sprawling biometric
OL,9,FID system is sinister, unjustified and
OL,10,Fprompts the chilling question of just
OL,11,Fwhat Starmer's government think the
OL,12,Fdigital ID will be used for in the
OL,13,Ffuture.
OL,15,F"At a time when parents are taking a
OL,16,Fcritical view of whether children
OL,17,Fshould have smart phones, it is
OL,18,Fshocking that the government is
OL,19,Fconsidering enrolling children into
OL,20,Fthis digital ID app.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
