OL,6,F"We now know that digital IDs could be
OL,7,Fused for everything from tax and
OL,8,Fbenefits to banking and education. It
OL,9,Fhas all the hallmarks of a sprawling
OL,10,Fnational database that Britain has
OL,11,Flong rejected.
OL,13,F"We urge parliamentarians to listen to
OL,14,Fthe concerns of millions of people in
OL,15,Fthis country and reject Starmer's
OL,16,Fmandatory digital ID."
