OL,6,FPrime Minister Starmer defended
OL,7,Fdigital ID cards while speaking during
OL,8,Fan official visit to India, saying
OL,9,Fthey are one of the "measures
OL,10,Fnecessary to grip" illegal migration.
OL,12,FHe added: "We have made a commitment
OL,13,Fto do whatever we can to stop people
OL,14,Farriving illegally in the United
OL,15,FKingdom. One of the issues is the
OL,16,Fability people have to work illegally
OL,17,Fin our economy. We have to do
OL,18,Fsomething about that. We can't shirk
OL,19,Fthat or duck that.
